Coming events at Turkey Creek
Spring Art Show
FREE
Saturday, April 5 - 8:30 am to 2:30 pm
Join us at the Tony Rosa Community Center, across the parking lot from the Sanctuary, for our Fall Art Show. We have 66 local vendors selling handcrafted items and our famous hot dog lunch featuring a hot dog, drink and chips.
Turkey Creek Day
FREE
Saturday, April 19 - 8:30 am to 3 pm
A FREE family fun day!
Local craft vendors - Environmental Groups
Children's storytime, with a special guest
Games for the kids - Balloon Twister
Scavenger hunt - Nature Tours
Our famous hot dog lunch featuring a hot dog, drink and a bag of chips, will be on sale.
Kids to Park Day
FREE
Saturday, May 17 - 9 to 10am
Join us for a special kids hike in the Sanctuary. The hike will include a visit to "tortoise town" to talk about these amazing reptiles. Parents are asked to join their children for this tour.
Park after Dark
FREE
SAVE THE DATE
Saturday, November, 15 - 6 to 9:30 pm
Our third annual event. Live music, vendors, food trucks and lots of fun.
